    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想做一个关于POSIX工具的思维导图，核心是展示这些工具的三大用途：过滤、转换和编程。根节点就叫'POSIX tools'吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((POSIX tools))",
        "Filtering",
        "Transforming",
        "Programming"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三大分支。那过滤这一类下面具体放哪些工具？grep肯定要有吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Filtering",
        "grep"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，过滤下面放grep、sed和AWK。然后转换这一类，sed和AWK也能做，所以放这两个。编程这块主要就是AWK了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "grep",
        "sed",
        "AWK",
        "Transforming",
        "Programming"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：Filtering分支有grep、sed、AWK；Transforming分支有sed、AWK；Programming分支只有AWK。这样sed和AWK会出现在多个分支下，没问题吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sed",
        "AWK",
        "Filtering",
        "Transforming",
        "Programming"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这正是我想表达的——sed和AWK是多面手工具，跨类别使用。图的结构就这样定了吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "sed",
        "AWK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，思维导图已经画好了。根节点是POSIX tools，三个一级分支分别是Filtering、Transforming和Programming，工具按我们讨论的分布好了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root((POSIX tools))",
        "Filtering",
        "Transforming",
        "Programming",
        "grep",
        "sed",
        "AWK"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Programming这个分支名我想调整一下，用'gramming'不太对，应该是完整的'Programming'。另外根节点的显示样式确认是圆角括号包裹吗？",
